everything about Jenna plus was cool.

257
00:10:23,539 --> 00:10:25,208
Bitch.

258
00:10:25,374 --> 00:10:27,210
So what are you in
detention for, wonder boy?

259
00:10:27,376 --> 00:10:29,337
I was caught holding
the hose at the bonfire.

260
00:10:29,503 --> 00:10:32,048
- Kinky.
- [Laughs] Yeah.

261
00:10:32,214 --> 00:10:33,806
And your crime, Hamilton?

262
00:10:33,931 --> 00:10:36,010
Oh, just a little...

263
00:10:38,637 --> 00:10:40,223
[Ahem] Misunderstanding.

264
00:10:40,389 --> 00:10:42,517
At lunch.
What are you in for?

265
00:10:42,683 --> 00:10:44,394
I'm a detention
rewards card member.

266
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:45,851
Today I blew off history

267
00:10:45,976 --> 00:10:47,897
'cause I was on the phone having
a meltdown with this guy.

268
00:10:48,063 --> 00:10:49,355
Was she talking about Matty,

269
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,693
or was I having a paranoia stroke?

270
00:10:51,859 --> 00:10:53,152
[Cell phone tune]

271
00:10:53,318 --> 00:10:54,904
Speak of the devil.

272
00:10:55,070 --> 00:10:56,585
What?

273
00:10:58,031 --> 00:10:59,993
No!

274
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,536
What does that even mean?

275
00:11:03,426 --> 00:11:05,070
Can I bum a smoke?

276
00:11:05,195 --> 00:11:06,499
Sure.

277
00:11:06,665 --> 00:11:08,440
I wondered
if Matty liked smokers.

278
00:11:08,565 --> 00:11:10,712
And if so, could I fake a pro?

279
00:11:10,878 --> 00:11:11,963
Okay, then why don't you
take your sweet ass time

280
00:11:12,129 --> 00:11:13,506
to think about it and call me back?

281
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,219
[Coughs]

282
00:11:19,636 --> 00:11:21,681
Everything okay?

283
00:11:21,847 --> 00:11:23,141
Yeah. It's just my ex.

284
00:11:23,307 --> 00:11:24,642
We've been on a break,

285
00:11:24,808 --> 00:11:27,312
and we're in the process
of maybe getting back together.

286
00:11:27,478 --> 00:11:29,161
Did that mean
I was Matty's rebound?

287
00:11:29,286 --> 00:11:30,982
Breaks are hard.

288
00:11:31,148 --> 00:11:32,775
Someone always hooks up
with another person,

289
00:11:32,941 --> 00:11:34,066
maybe even falls for them.

290
00:11:34,191 --> 00:11:35,486
Think he's into someone else?

291
00:11:35,652 --> 00:11:39,271
I thought so.
But now I'm not so sure.

292
00:11:39,396 --> 00:11:41,607
When we're together, it's...
It's amazing.

293
00:11:41,732 --> 00:11:42,910
It's like...

294
00:11:43,076 --> 00:11:45,621
The world falls away...
Then the next day,

295
00:11:45,787 --> 00:11:47,479
